{"tid":589672,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"轉工","createTime":"2018-03-12T04:18:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-12T04:40:26.000Z","uid":148724,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"698f666d0244af5ee9b194901ac23642dc512d1f","tid":589672,"uid":148724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T04:18:16.000Z","msg":"早兩個月做annual review, 人工加得小小, 不過花紅多<br />\n<br />\n但係都覺得自己值多D, 所以就開始apply 工<br />\n<br />\n呢1,2個月開始有interview , 唔知係咪而家老細sense到我有離心<br />\n所有就升左我職 (係細公司都叫有D話事權), 仲加多我小小人工<br />\n<br />\n同時間又收到另一間公司既offer,大公司<br />\n<br />\n舊公司: 中等人工 + 大份bonus (迷你公司, 個人發展應該較好)<br />\n新公司: 高人工 + 13月糧 (超大型公司, 穩穩定定)<br />\n<br />\noverall 年薪計落其實差唔多<br />\n大家會點揀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c666ee4b2890bdab207382b05941f7eaf30254d4","tid":589672,"uid":8867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T04:20:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"acc1785d8d22c0759a3ca0ed8593b72484c5a909","tid":589672,"uid":17641,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T04:22:26.000Z","msg":"辭職炒股入騰訊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2be3fdf9d7b65d2bd3f83429ca5a9aa66e5a3d74","tid":589672,"uid":142707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T04:24:53.000Z","msg":"睇下邊個會升得高d<br />\n升既時間邊邊快d<br />\n<br />\n要睇前途"},{"pid":"dcb4de3f065488a82589a29007b2be1b2bb6e8f1","tid":589672,"uid":14566,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T04:25:54.000Z","msg":"本身咩post先<br />\n細公司搵3-4皮可能就到頂<br />\n大公司搵3-4皮只係mid level<br />\n<br />\n不過魚唔過塘唔肥，keep住轉工一定升得快過同一間公司慢慢排隊上"},{"pid":"18dfa37c51c83a184e38615669978c1314b54022","tid":589672,"uid":148724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c666ee4b2890bdab207382b05941f7eaf30254d4","tid":589672,"uid":8867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T04:20:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T04:28:02.000Z","msg":